quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  17,85,"Wọ́n ń bi ọ́ léèrè nípa ẹ̀mí. Sọ pé: “Ẹ̀mí ń bẹ nínú àṣẹ Olúwa mi. A ò sì fun yín nínú ìmọ̀ bí kò ṣe díẹ̀.”"
  17,86,"Àti pé dájúdájú tí A bá fẹ́ ni, A ìbá kúkú gba ìmísí tí A fi ránṣẹ́ sí ọ (kúrò ní ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ). Lẹ́yìn náà, ìwọ kò níí rí aláàbò kan tí ó máa là ọ́ lọ́dọ̀ Wa"
  17,87,Àyàfi ìkẹ́ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ (ni kò fi ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀). Dájúdájú oore àjùlọ Rẹ̀ lórí rẹ tóbi
  17,88,"Sọ pé: “Dájúdájú tí àwọn ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú bá para pọ̀ láti mú irú al-Ƙur’ān yìí wá, wọn kò lè mú irú rẹ̀ wá, apá kan wọn ìbáà jẹ́ olùrànlọ́wọ́ fún apá kan"
  17,89,Dájúdájú A ti fi àkàwé kọ̀ọ̀kan ṣàlàyé (oríṣiríṣi) fún àwọn ènìyàn sínú al-Ƙur’ān yìí. Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ ènìyàn kọ̀ láti gbà àfi àtakò sá
  17,90,"Wọ́n sì wí pé: “A kò níí gbà ọ́ gbọ́ títí o máa fi mú omi ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú ṣẹ́ yọ fún wa"
  17,91,"Tàbí kí o ní ọgbà oko dàbínù àti ọgbà oko àjàrà, tí o sì máa jẹ́ kí àwọn odò ṣàn kọ já dáadáa láààrin wọn"
  17,92,Tàbí kí o jẹ́ kí sánmọ̀ já lù wá ní kélekèle gẹ́gẹ́ bí o ṣe sọ (pé Allāhu lè ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀). Tàbí kí o mú Allāhu àti àwọn mọlāika wá (bá wa) ní ojúkojú
  17,93,"Tàbí kí o ní ilé wúrà kan, tàbí kí o gun òkè sánmọ̀ lọ. A kò sì níí gba gígun-sánmọ̀ rẹ gbọ́ títí o fi máa sọ tírà kan tí a óò máa ké kalẹ̀ fún wa.” Sọ pé: “Mímọ́ ni fún Olúwa mi, ǹjẹ́ mo jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe Òjíṣẹ́ abara?”"